00:18:22.120 --> 00:18:26.390
And you know, I like slaying
dragons or at least trying to.

00:18:26.390 --> 00:18:28.600
&gt;&gt; Colleen Shogan: In 2007 --
we are the Library of Congress,

00:18:28.600 --> 00:18:30.580
so we like to talk about books.

00:18:30.580 --> 00:18:33.560
