00:23:34.240 --> 00:23:37.480
Have you seen an effect
by your approach?

00:23:37.480 --> 00:23:40.380
&gt;&gt; Rep. Jackie Speier: I
so first realized the power

00:23:40.380 --> 00:23:44.120
